0.003   2020-02-19  Released-By: PERLANCAR; Urgency: medium

	- Switch algorithm to using buckets like in Data::Throttler, because
          recording every hit as a cache item quickly becomes too slow when the
          number of hits reaches thousands. We are now consistently about an
          order of magnitude slower than Data::Throttler when both are using
          memory backend.


0.002   2020-02-19  Released-By: PERLANCAR; Urgency: medium

	- [doc] Tweak/fix example in Synopsis.

	- [optimize] No need to sprintf().


0.001   2020-02-19  Released-By: PERLANCAR

        - First release.
